Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反對融合個體！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\1c&H204473&\be2\bord1\pos(942,10)}別忘了100年前的悲劇！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反對融合個體！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白天的時間有點變短了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要求軍隊司令部撤銷非常事態宣言！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤銷！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融合個體就是奇居子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓奇居子進入希德尼婭！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別讓奇居子進入希德尼婭！
